      <title>英特尔首席执行官离职为新交易谈判打开大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/intel-s-ceo-departure-opens-door-to-fresh-deal-discussions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司首席执行官帕特·基辛格的突然离职为这家陷入困境的公司提供了一个新的机会来考虑潜在的交易选择，包括他在执掌这家芯片制造商期间拒绝的方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/intel-s-ceo-departure-opens-door-to-fresh-deal-discussions</guid>
