    <item>
      <title>购物者在网络星期一花费 133 亿美元，比 2023 年增长 7.3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/cyber-monday-13-5-billion-splurge-seen-beating-initial-forecast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Adobe Inc. 的数据显示，美国购物者在“网络星期一”的网上消费额为 133 亿美元，较 2023 年增长 7.3%，略高于该公司最初预测的 132 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/cyber-monday-13-5-billion-splurge-seen-beating-initial-forecast</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 00:08:52 GMT</pubDate>
